    <td><p><keyseq><key>Super</key><key>H</key></keyseq></p></td>
    <td><p>Minimize a window.</p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><p><keyseq><key>Super</key><key>←</key></keyseq></p></td>
    <td><p>Maximize a window vertically along the left side of the screen.
